                            <comment id="14583544" author="gnt" created="Fri, 12 Jun 2015 15:11:05 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Yeah, of course, sorry about that. It seems &quot;git svn dcommit&quot; only send a single commit...&lt;br/&gt;
